        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Lim Hyeon-Jun (Lee Jung-Jae) is a popular actor. He specializes in playing detective characters, but he dreams of becoming master actor of melodrama. Meanwhile, Wi Jeong-Sin (Lim Ji-Yeon) is an ace reporter of politics and won a youngest reporter award. She becomes caught up in a big corruption scandal and loses her position in the politics department. She ends up being assigned to the entertainment department and tries to adjust there. Lim Hyeon-Jun and Wi Jeong-Sin get involved with each other. They try to overcome their own prejudice and change gradually.",
